_sText:
This isn't a large map.  We played 12 on 12 and it got pleasantly chaotic.  It has spawns for up to 20 on each team.  If you put int on a server that large expect maximum carnage in short order.  Anyways enjoy



I inclued nav file that goes with bsp in your maps folder other files go in your SteamApps folder if you want to tinker with the vmf stuff
